"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"3min 全港airtime 真係唔好浪費黎同條八婆講嘢"},{"pid":"63a0d4f7991571083b85a2c9f60039f8e0f55ad3","tid":1597371,"uid":226896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"同意，推！<br />\n免費電視廣告！<br />\n有人話應該杯葛等佢地圍爐，冇機會俾佢地有多種聲音嘅畫面，你估咁樣佢地仲播唔播？整幾個入去喬裝中立淺黃有何難？"},{"pid":"cec44661c1c0558c21196ff72b3d2538b4112671","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63a0d4f7991571083b85a2c9f60039f8e0f55ad3","tid":1597371,"uid":226896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"同意，推！<br />\n免費電視廣告！<br />\n有人話應該杯葛等佢地圍爐，冇機會俾佢地有多種聲音嘅畫面，你估咁樣佢地仲播唔播？整幾個入去喬裝中立淺黃有何難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"岩，所以就算唔認同利用對話會，認為要「杯葛」對話會既手足。<br />\n我覺得至少報個名，不出席，令少啲藍絲／假中立／假黃抽中。"},{"pid":"b4cf5db041bd2149ab841309d6910c074d417f44","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efa25e8111dc0e7d69d2798a8903234b87ed6a93","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:23:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6bcc797469216b8e713d8c637e8303bc6e4612ce","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7b709ca90084824d92e669f9e2773a5b7b9ca9a","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"928 101"},{"pid":"284844d2bf17e420e6d9e3024cd28c8f327c0301","tid":1597371,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:54:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4863deaaebbc75bf9a53bc9e82f5f97987c162c","tid":1597371,"uid":282919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"問下幾時起新彊再教育營？<br />\n李家超咁贊成，又派人去考察，到時個營起响邊？"}]}